\b\fs46 \cf3 Flour\uc0\u8232 
\b0\fs42 \cf0 Instead of: 1 cup self-rising flour\uc0\u8232 You can use: 1 cup all-purpose flour plus 1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder and 1/8 teaspoon salt\
Instead of: 1 cup cake flour\uc0\u8232 You can use: 1 cup minus 2 tablespoons all-purpose flour\
Instead of: 1 cup whole-wheat flour\uc0\u8232 You can use: 7/8 cup all-purpose flour plus 2 tablespoons wheat germ\

\b\fs46 \cf3 Brown Sugar and Molasses\uc0\u8232 
\b0\fs42 \cf0 Instead of: 1 cup light-brown sugar\uc0\u8232 You can use: 1 cup white sugar plus 1 1/2 tablespoons molasses\
Instead of: 1 cup molasses\uc0\u8232 You can use: 3/4 cup dark-brown sugar plus 1/4 cup water\
